client'\r
import React, { SetStateAction } from 'react'\r
import { useState } from 'react'\r
import { AnimatePresence, motion } from 'framer-motion'\r
const items = [\r
  {\r
    id: '5',\r
    url: 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dzl9yxixg/image/upload/v1714741157/photo-1714402002623-86d68590c545_eyrfna.jpg',\r
    title: 'Snow-Capped Serenity',\r
    description:\r
      'Snow blankets the high mountain peaks, offering a serene and pristine white canvas against the crisp blue sky.',\r
    tags: ['Snow-Capped', 'Serenity', 'Pristine', 'Blue Sky', 'High Peaks'],\r
  },\r
\r
  {\r
    id: '7',\r
    url: 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dzl9yxixg/image/upload/v1714741157/photo-1712313242836-3ae9c1fd6767_ynpin3.jpg',\r
    title: 'Verdant Valley Vista',\r
    description:\r
      'A lush green valley nestled between mountains, bathed in the warm light of a setting sun, offering a tranquil retreat.',\r
    tags: ['Verdant', 'Valley', 'Vista', 'Tranquil', 'Sunset'],\r
  },\r
  {\r
    id: '8',\r
    url: 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dzl9yxixg/image/upload/v1714741157/photo-1714523479594-13c0bb72fcf3_n85lma.jpg',\r
    title: 'Rocky Ridges',\r
    description:\r
      'The rugged ridges of the mountain form a stark contrast against the soft clouds above, embodying the spirit of adventure.',\r
    tags: ['Rocky', 'Ridges', 'Contrast', 'Adventure', 'Clouds'],\r
  },\r
\r
  {\r
    id: '6',\r
    url: 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dzl9yxixg/image/upload/v1714741157/photo-1713223289172-e45b0ed96eae_cdizhk.jpg',\r
    title: 'Floral Highlands',\r
    description:\r
      'Amidst the rugged mountainous terrain, bursts of wildflowers add a splash of color, showcasing nature\u2019s resilience.',\r
    tags: ['Floral', 'Highlands', 'Wildflowers', 'Colorful', 'Resilience'],\r
  },\r
  {\r
    id: '9',\r
    url: 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dzl9yxixg/image/upload/v1714741157/photo-1714312634720-ae1f906d09d6_hoslf5.jpg',\r
    title: 'Twilight Peaks',\r
    description:\r
      'As twilight descends, the peaks of the mountains are silhouetted against a gradient evening sky, creating a peaceful end to the day.',\r
    tags: ['Twilight', 'Peaks', 'Silhouette', 'Evening Sky', 'Peaceful'],\r
  },\r
]\r
const article = {\r
  hidden: { opacity: 0, y: 20 },\r
  show: {\r
    opacity: 1,\r
    y: 0,\r
    transition: {\r
      type: 'spring',\r
      stiffness: 100,\r
      delayChildren: 0.2,\r
      staggerChildren: 0.1, // Stagger duration for children\r
    },\r
  },\r
}\r
\r
type item = {\r
  id: string\r
  url: string\r
  title: string\r
  description: string\r
  tags?: string[]\r
}\r
interface GaleryProps {\r
  items: item[]\r
  setIndex: React.Dispatch<SetStateAction<number>>\r
  index: number | undefined\r
}\r
function Gallery({ items, setIndex, index }: GaleryProps) {\r
  return (\r
    <div className="w-fit mx-auto gap-1 flex pb-20 pt-10 ">\r
      {items.map((item: item, i: number) => {\r
        return (\r
          <motion.div\r
            whileTap={{ scale: 0.95 }}\r
            className={\`rounded-xl relative \${\r
              index === i ? 'w-[450px] ' : 'w-[50px]'\r
            } h-[400px] flex-shrink-0  transition-[width] ease-in-linear duration-500 origin-center  \`}\r
            key={i}\r
            onClick={() => {\r
              setIndex(i)\r
            }}\r
          >\r
            <motion.img\r
              src={item?.url}\r
              className={\`\${\r
                index === i ? 'cursor-default' : 'cursor-pointer'\r
              } w-full rounded-xl  h-full object-cover \`}\r
            />\r
            <AnimatePresence mode="wait">\r
              {index === i && (\r
                <motion.article\r
                  variants={article}\r
                  initial="hidden"\r
                  animate="show"\r

}\r
